"Firstly, some ascetic or brahmin—by dint of keen, resolute, committed, and "
"diligent effort, and right focus—experiences an immersion of the heart of "
"such a kind that they recollect many hundreds of thousands of past lives,"

msgctxt "dn28:44.4"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn28:44.5"
msgid ""
"tathārūpaṃ cetosamādhiṃ phusati, yathāsamāhite citte anekavihitaṃ "
"pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn28:44.6"
msgid "Seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn28:44.7"
msgid ""
"ekampi jātiṃ dvepi jātiyo tissopi jātiyo catassopi jātiyo pañcapi jātiyo "
"dasapi jātiyo vīsampi jātiyo tiṃsampi jātiyo cattālīsampi jātiyo paññāsampi "
"jātiyo jātisatampi jātisahassampi jātisatasahassampi anekānipi jātisatāni "
"anekānipi jātisahassāni anekānipi jātisatasahassāni, ‘amutrāsiṃ evaṃnāmo "
"evaṃgotto evaṃvaṇṇo evamāhāro evaṃsukhadukkhappaṭisaṃvedī evamāyupariyanto, "
"so tato cuto amutra udapādiṃ;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn28:44.8"
msgid ""
"tatrāpāsiṃ evaṃnāmo evaṃgotto evaṃvaṇṇo evamāhāro "
"evaṃsukhadukkhappaṭisaṃvedī evamāyupariyanto, so tato cuto idhūpapanno’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn28:44.9"
msgid "Iti sākāraṃ sauddesaṃ anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati."
msgstr "with features and details."

msgctxt "dn28:44.10"
msgid "So evamāha:"
msgstr "They say:"

msgctxt "dn28:44.11"
msgid "‘atītampāhaṃ addhānaṃ jānāmi—"
msgstr "‘I know that in the past the cosmos expanded or contracted."

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "dn28:44.12"
msgid "saṃvaṭṭi vā loko vivaṭṭi vāti."
msgstr " "

