msgid "Anāgataṃpāhaṃ addhānaṃ jānāmi—"
msgstr "I don’t know whether in the future the cosmos will expand or contract."

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "dn28:44.14"
msgid "saṃvaṭṭissati vā loko vivaṭṭissati vāti."
msgstr " "

msgctxt "dn28:44.15"
msgid "Sassato attā ca loko ca vañjho kūṭaṭṭho esikaṭṭhāyiṭṭhito."
msgstr ""
"The self and the cosmos are eternal, barren, steady as a mountain peak, "
"standing firm like a pillar."

msgctxt "dn28:44.16"
msgid ""
"Te ca sattā sandhāvanti saṃsaranti cavanti upapajjanti, atthi tveva "
"sassatisaman’ti."
msgstr ""
"They remain the same for all eternity, while these sentient beings wander "
"and transmigrate and pass away and rearise.’"

msgctxt "dn28:44.17"
msgid "Ayaṃ paṭhamo sassatavādo."
msgstr "This is the first eternalist doctrine."

